{"tid":2413953,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港即將為市民打科興疫苗 ，如果接種引致死亡或面癱，可獲賠償。","createTime":"2021-02-19T05:31:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-19T05:31:00.000Z","uid":318316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"81000872619bfcfcbd2b6479580ca63c429205f6","tid":2413953,"uid":318316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T05:31:00.000Z","msg":"香港26日起為市民施打科興疫苗 <br />\n<br />\n（中央社記者張謙香港18日電）香港當局將於2月26日起免費為特定人群施打2019冠狀病毒疾病（COVID-19，武漢肺炎）疫苗，全屬自願性質；<strong>如果接種引致死亡或面癱等，可獲賠償。</strong> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.cna.com.tw/amp/news/acn/202102180184.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Famp%2Fnews%2Facn%2F202102180184.aspx&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69OL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=28d1797a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.cna.com.tw/amp/news/acn/202102180184.aspx</a>"}]}